See http://mruckert.userweb.mwn.de/hint/web2w.html

Add the following to .bashrc:
  export SCREEN_SIZE=$(xrandr 2>/dev/null|grep connected|grep -o "[0-9]\+x[0-9]\+")

It is assumed that this repo is in /home/user/.

Use the companion repo http://github.com/igor-liferenko/mf-wayland

To use debugger, run "gdb plain" or
"NOWIN=1 gdb plain" or
"mv ~/mf-wayland/hello-wayland ~/mf-wayland/suppress-wayland; gdb plain"

To run METAFONT, use "exec /home/user/mf/plain"
